|-----------|-------|
| Curve | y² = x³ + 7 (mod p) |
| Field size p | 2²⁵⁶ - 2³² - 977 |
| Group order n | ~2²⁵⁶ |
| Classical security | 128 bits (Pollard's rho) |
| Logical qubits needed | ≥ 1,546 |
| Physical qubits needed | ≥ 4,638,000 |
